#: abdessalam-ai-toolkit-for-webmcp/abdessalam-ai-toolkit-for-webmcp.php:182
msgid ""
"Abdessalam AI Toolkit for WebMCP helps make your WordPress site easier for "
"AI agents and AI-enabled browsers to understand. Instead of forcing an "
"assistant to guess from the visual page, the plugin exposes clear "
"instructions, structured tools, and form labels that tell the agent what "
"actions are available and how to use them."
msgstr ""

